{
  "stem": "24130.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So these volunteer Jewish soldiers used to take us to a club by-- by trucks from the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Otherwise, we were still in a camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Still not free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no matter where we registered, the doors were just closed for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We still had to wait for a quota and waited.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we couldn't find my sister for a long time because my sister got married and she changed her name from-- from-- my sister that came from before the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She got married so her name was changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the place, we remembered the address.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the place where she lived, they threw down the houses and they built a project.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was no such Os-- street, like the Osborne Street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was Osborne Street, but there was no such number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So couldn't find my sister for about a year after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one of the soldiers, a Canadian, was coming to America, and we asked him if he could find our sister in America.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's funny, but-- but believe it or not, he did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He looked at us probably like we are crazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he didn't want to refuse us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Jack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took all the information from us, where we born, and he came to America and he put it in the news-- in the Jewish newspaper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And believe it or not, when he came back he gave me the letter with pictures from my sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how we found our sister here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't have to tell you-- she thought nobody survived-- to find three sisters alive, how she felt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then she sent us papers to come to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
